This paper deals with techniques for processing uncertain data in database systems, which is a core problem in the field of database management (cs.DB). The paper also introduces algorithms for building histogram- and wavelet-based synopses on probabilistic data, which involves analyzing the structure of probability distributions and devising efficient algorithms, making it relevant to the fields of data structures (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
